targets.query: SELECT sum("success") as deploys FROM "deploy" WHERE ("project" =~ /^$ProjectDeployName$/)  and ("releaseEnvironmentName" =~ /^$environment$/) AND $timeFilter  GROUP BY time(1d) , project

panels.title: Daily Deployment Frequency  - successful deployments - By ProjectDeployName / By Environment

targets.query: SELECT 100 - (mean("success") * 100) FROM "deploy" WHERE  ("project" =~ /^$ProjectDeployName$/) and ("releaseEnvironmentName" =~ /^$environment$/)  AND $timeFilter Group By time(1d), project

panels.title: Daily Deployment Failure Rate - By ProjectDeployName / By Environment

targets.query: select  mean(elap) from (select difference("success") as diff, elapsed("success",1h) as elap FROM "deploy"  where ("project" =~ /^$ProjectDeployName$/) and ("releaseEnvironmentName" =~ /^$environment$/) ) where diff > 0   group by project;

panels.title: Time to Restore Service (Deploy) - Mean elapsed time between failure and success - By ProjectDeployName / By Environment

targets.query: SELECT  sum from ( select sum("duration") FROM "workitem"   where ("type" =~ /^$WorkItemType$/)  AND ("state" =~ /^$workItemState$/)  AND ("project" =~ /^$workitemproject$/) group by  title ) where title != '' group by title;

panels.title: Lead Time for Changes by WorkItemType / by workItemState / by workitemproject
